---
import { Award, Zap, Shield, Lightbulb, Users, CheckCircle } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Legionella Water Schematics: Precision CAD Services
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        HSE guidelines (HSG 274 Part 2) mandate Legionella Schematic Drawings as essential components 
        of prudent risk management programs. Our CAD services deliver precision-engineered solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <!-- Content Side -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            HSG 274 Part 2 Compliance
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            These schematic drawings are simplified yet precise diagrams that identify the layout 
            of building water systems, machinery, equipment, and components. Designed to be easily 
            comprehensible without specialized training.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-blue-100 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-blue-800 text-sm font-medium">
              âœ“ All temporary fixtures must be included, even short-term installations 
              like temporary washing machines that can impact water quality.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-cyan-100">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Digital Format Flexibility
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            High-quality CAD schematic diagrams delivered in various digital formats, 
            facilitating their use in enhancing on-site risk management, safety engineering, 
            and document control procedures.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Side -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092334651-ddf26d9a09d0?w=600&h=500&fit=crop&crop=entropy&auto=format&q=80"
            alt="Professional CAD workstation"
            class="w-full h-96 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-lg"
          />
          <!-- Floating Badge -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 text-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold">CAD</div>
              <div class="text-xs">Precision</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">
        Why Choose CAD Outsource for Legionella CAD Services?
      </h3>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <Award className="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">Expertise</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Specialized team with in-depth knowledge of Legionella risk management and CAD standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="bg-cyan-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <Zap className="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-600" />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">Precision</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Accurate and detailed Legionella water schematics for effective risk mitigation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="bg-green-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <Shield className="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">Compliance</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Designs aligned with industry regulations for legal and ecological responsibility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="bg-indigo-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <Lightbulb className="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">Innovation</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Integration of advanced 3D modeling for enhanced visualization and planning.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Our CAD Schematics -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our CAD Schematics</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Our company excels at creating detailed drawings of water systems with guaranteed accuracy. 
            We've created comprehensive schematics for diverse facilities including schools, hospitals, 
            factories with cooling towers, universities, care homes, and other public buildings.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-slate-300">Time and cost savings for surveyors</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-slate-300">Professional CAD quality vs. basic Visio drawings</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-slate-300">Comprehensive facility coverage</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-slate-300">Existing schematic review and updates</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
            <Users className="w-16 h-16 text-blue-400 mx-auto mb-6" />
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">500+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-300 mb-4">Facilities Mapped</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              From educational institutions to healthcare facilities and industrial complexes
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>